<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Beautiful Image Signature</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .imgsig {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    img:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="imgsig">
    <H1>กราบขอบคุณอาจารย์เป็นอย่างสูง</H1>
    <img src="/img/OIP.jpg" alt="Image description" title="Image title">
  </div>
</body>
</html>